Quickstrike:





"Don't do it again," Quickstrike said. "Pointless." he mumbled. "Ah don't 
wanna see ya hurt." He shook his head, then let go. He walked back to the 
others. "Dang crazy females."

He saw Megatron ahead. "Boss!" he said. "There ya are."
